# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2025-01-08
### Added
- Initial release of fleet management system
- Route optimization using machine learning models
- Real-time vehicle tracking and telemetry
- Driver behavior analysis and scoring system
- Predictive maintenance forecasting using historical data
- REST API endpoints for fleet data access
- Authentication and authorization system
- Dashboard for fleet performance metrics

### Fixed
- Memory leak in the telemetry data collection service
- Edge case handling in route optimization algorithm
- Time zone conversion issues in reporting module

### Changed
- Upgraded TensorFlow dependencies to version 2.15
- Improved ML model architecture for better prediction accuracy
- Enhanced data preprocessing pipeline
- Optimized database queries for better performance

### Security
- Implemented rate limiting for API endpoints
- Added input validation for all user-submitted data
- Enhanced encryption for sensitive vehicle data

## [0.9.0] - 2024-12-15
### Added
- Beta release of core functionality
- Basic route planning capabilities
- Vehicle status monitoring
- Simple reporting features

### Changed
- Refactored database schema for better scalability
- Updated UI components for improved user experience

### Deprecated
- Legacy CSV export format (will be removed in 1.1.0)

## [0.8.0] - 2024-11-30
### Added
- Alpha testing release
- Proof of concept ML models
- Basic API structure

